text: Walewska may refer to: * Walewska Oliveira (born 1979), Brazilian volleyball player * Małgorzata Walewska (born 1965), Polish opera singer * Marie Walewska (1786–1817), Polish noblewoman and a mistress of Napoleon * Marie-Anne Walewska (1823–1912), French courtier and a mistress of Napoleon III * Countess Walewska, a 1914 Polish historical film
title: Walewska
